text: Olga Osipyan (; born 2 September 1995) is an Armenian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Ukrainian Women's League club Voskhod Stara Mayachka and the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Osipyan capped most recently for Armenia at senior level in two friendlies against Lithuania on 4 and 6 March 2020. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers Category:Russian Women's Football Championship players Category:Armenian expatriate footballers Category:Armenian expatriate sportspeople in Russia Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Russia Category:Armenian expatriate sportspeople in Kazakhstan Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Kazakhstan Category:Armenian expatriate sportspeople in Ukraine Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Ukraine
